extends layout

block content
  h1= title
    p Welcome to #[em LocalLibrary], a very basic Express website developed as a tutorial example on the Mozilla Developer Network.


    h1 Dynamic content

    if error
      p Error getting dynamic content.

    p This book has the following record below :

    ul
      li book stored : #BookStoredNumber
      li book copied : #BookCopiedNumber
      li book copied available : #BookAvaiableNumber
      li total book author : #AuthorNumber
      li total book genre : #GenresNumber